wbar (2.4.0)

  * I adopt derived version of wbar by Ivan Fitenko, at:
       https://github.com/ivanfitenko/wbar
    and cloned it to
       https://github.com/hmatrjp/wbar
    then start overhaul.
      
  * Default prefix is set to /usr/local in autogen.sh:
     so Debian packaged version and original can be installed in parallel
  * Applied Debian patches:
    - gcc-6-literal-suffix.patch
    - remove-GNOME2_DIR.patch
    - no-AC_SUBST-pidof.patch
    - autoconf-2.70.patch
    - configure.ac.patch
    - gettext.patch
  * Replace the UI XML from old GLADE to newer one
    - This is done by gtk-builder-ui.patch posted at Debian Bug#1090851
  * Transition of use of deprecated GDK functions:
    - gdk_color_parse() to gdk_rgba_parse()
    - gtk_popup_menu() to gdk_popup_menu_at_pointer()
  * Added initial Japanese Translation

 -- Takeshi Hamasaki <Takeshi.Ken.Hamasaki+hmatrjp@gmail.com> (21-12-2025)

